# Cloudflare Pages HTTP headers for magic machine routes.
#
# COOP/COEP headers (required for SharedArrayBuffer) are NOT enabled here because
# ken-burns-zoom-builder uses @ffmpeg/core (single-threaded) which does not need
# SharedArrayBuffer. Enabling require-corp without crossorigin attributes on all
# CDN resources breaks script loading.
#
# If upgrading to @ffmpeg/core-mt (multi-threaded), re-add:
#   Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
#   Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
# AND add crossorigin="anonymous" to all cross-origin <script> and <link> tags.
